        "title": "User Grievance Mechanisms",
        "text": "Field Value Variable Id exchange-cred-grievance Definition Mechanisms for government agencies and citizens to report issues, lodge complaints, or seek redress regarding data exchange Format Text (400 characters max); \"NA\" if unknown or not applicable Other Metadata Include helpdesk, ombudsman, escalation procedures, response time SLAs Data Collection Guidelines Review service delivery complaint mechanisms, public protector mandates, digital services helpdesk documentation, service charters",
